Welcome to Model Now, the only model app you need to collaborate with
professionals within the modeling industry on the go.

Model Now is the official app of ModelManagement.com, the worldwide platform
where models and talents find jobs and creatives find models.

+ 1.6 Million models registered + Over 273k brands, photographers, modeling
agencies and other industry professionals

**Download Model Now, the best app of all casting apps you will find!**

DO YOU WANT TO MODEL?


Model Now is the perfect app to find online casting calls. Whether you are a
newcomer, professional model or influencer, you will be able to apply to
hundreds of castings all over the world with just one click.

Create your model portfolio just in a few seconds and get discovered by
photographers, modeling agencies, brands and clients.

- Create your online model portfolio
- Find model auditions
- Apply to castings in a few seconds
- Send messages to model
photographers and other industry professionals
- Paid jobs and collaborations
- Safe platform for all models and talents


DO YOU WANT TO FIND MODELS?


If you are looking for models, influencers and content creators for your next
professional photoshoot, Model Now is the app you need.

Create a casting, explain the profile you’re looking for and get hundreds of
applicants in the blink of an eye!

- Create a casting call in a few minutes

- Invite models and talents that fit the requirements

- Select the models

- Get in touch with the selected ones

- TFP and paid projects

Download Model Now, the best option for your model photography!


MORE ABOUT MODELMANAGEMENT.COM


ModelManagement.com is the worldwide platform that connects new faces,
professional models and talents with brands, photographers and content
creators.

On one hand, aspiring and professional models, as well as talents, can apply
to thousands of castings worldwide, learn with the Model Academy and join a
safe platform where all members are manually verified.

On the other hand, photographers and other creatives can find models and
talents for their projects, connect with other industry professionals and
manage their projects from beginning to end, including contracts and payments.
We aim to encourage the success of starting and small businesses looking for
an efficient and highly effective way of creating marketing campaigns, give
personality to their brand, or find an artistic outline to engage in. Our
dedicated team of professionals has over 30 years of experience within the
industry, from the catwalks of Milan to designing IT systems for premier model
agencies in Europe.


WHO CAN USE MODEL NOW?


Everyone can join our community! At ModelManagement.com we give everyone the
opportunity to get started in this industry, no matter their age, height, size
or background. We are modeling for everyone.

IS IT JUST FOR MODELS?


No. On ModelManagement.com you will find new faces, professional models,
hostesses, real life people, talents and everything in-between. So, if you are
a singer, dancer, influencer, content creator, actor… you can join us! We are
more than models.
